page.title: 06LIFE STYLES
page.content:
REV.MAC DONALD MILNE
We interviewed Rev.Mac Donald Milne.The first question we asked him was"Would you like the village to be changed in any way".He answered that question by saying this"Yes there is plenty of things".Another question was"How long have you been doing your job".Rev.Mac Donald Milne answered"I have been working for two years".The next question we asked him was"Is there anything important happening in your village over the next few weeks". The answer that he gave us was"Yes there is going to be a fete".He gave us lots of intresting answers about the village of Landbeach.
